Package com.pandora.general.services.calculation.implementations

Class CellTimestepServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
com.pandora.general.services.calculation.implementations.CellTimestepServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
CellTimestepService
@Service public class CellTimestepServiceImpl extends Object implements CellTimestepService
The CellTimestepServiceImpl class implements the CellTimestepService interface and provides functionality for calculating the time series of cell timesteps in the Pandora model. It utilizes various services, including those for accessing and manipulating Y values, terrestrial sources, upstream sources, discharges, volumes, as well as services for integrating Pandora timesteps and managing local date and time operations.

This class uses the Spring Framework's @Service annotation to indicate that it is a service component and can be injected into other components.
